reviews.review_text: I m here from the states for a touring contract and my card has been on the fritz. The manager gave me some food so I could eat and figure out my situation. She was really lovely and helped me in a sticky situation. The location is clean and the food is good, and this was a really sweet gesture. Thank you so much!

Had breakfast here the other day. My husbands sausage Mcmuffin was super fresh and tasty. I tried the cinnamon raisin bagel with cream cheese. It was delicious, perfectly toasted and tons of cream cheese. Much better than Tim Hortons! Great location, very clean restaurant and washrooms. Highly recommend

Very clean and Very good food. Staff were happy and smiling lots creating a really welcoming and family friendly atmosphere. Also the washrooms were clean and well stocked. The wifi was easy to log into. And the service was speedily efficient.. and McDonald s has the best fries

McDonalds is a great fast food restaurant. The food is always cooked fresh and tastes great. The service is usually quick and friendly. I enjoy their variety of burgers and fries. The prices are very reasonable and they often have great deals. The restaurant is always clean and the staff is always friendly. I also like that they offer a variety of healthy options like salads and fruit smoothies. I also appreciate that they offer a drive-thru option so I can get my food quickly. Overall, I highly recommend McDonalds for anyone looking for a quick, tasty and affordable meal.

The staff was amazing they were short staffed but everyone got their orders. Not sure of the managers name but she had to deal with a very rude customer. She did an awesome job keeping her cool while this guy berated her in front of others because he had to wait a whole 7 minutes for his order. I figure if you cant wait dont stop in.

This was one of my first times getting McDonalds though 3rd party delivery. My food was fast, fresh and hot. All items were in the bag, presented properly. Tamper proof seal and requested condiments were all done correctly. These are all reasons that help keep me confident in ordering food from 3rd party. By the way, everything was delicious!

Disappointed in the food today, but the customer care  from the general manager has set a new standard Ive never received before. Thanks for your care, kindness and attention to detail. I will return to this location specifically because of the outstanding customer service. 10 stars from me! Thank you

The whole staff is amazing and I went during a really busy time (I think a nearby highschool was out for lunch break)  but the staff remained composed and served everyone quickly.  I think the managers Brandon and Leanne were pitching in as well.  One of the best run McDonalds that Ive seen.
Food was okay. But girl working on drive thru on 17th of Sep(SaturdAy evening shift)needs to learn some customer service skills. I hope this review will be helpful to improve your service. Thanks

I had a great experience at this McDonalds! I just went through the drive thru right now and even though I changed my order at the first window, they were accurate and fast. The lady in the first window is so kind and bright! Fazi the manager at the second window is so attentive. I ve never had a better interaction with a McDonalds in surrey!
Usually the food here is cold and drive through has long waits. But this day was fresh fries and amazing food. No line ups.

I had a great experience. The staff is really nice and helpful. I came in drive thru and I got my order fresh and tasty. The managers are accommodating and I always feel welcomed.. that s why I come again and again. Thank you guys. G

This McDonalds is 500m away from me and Im so grateful for how much they have improved over the last couple of months. The quality of the food, the freshness and quickness has significantly improved. Thank you to all staff and managers here for the consistent great experiences! I encourage everyone to visit this mcdonalds over any other near by

Amazing service by the whole team. I visited this location most of the time. I like their quick service and they always serve fresh and good quality food. One day I went to drive through and i observed that the staff members are very nice. Most of the time I get my food through gursimran and fazzilat, they both are very nice and dedicated to their work. I wanna recommend  to everyone to visit this place. I can say you will definitely get great services from them.

People are so kind with their customers. So friendly environment. Mostly I visit this location always feel so good. I always get good food their quality is great. I like their quick service. Great experience. Keep going team.

Amazing service by team. People are so kind with their customers. I went yesterday, my food is so hot and fresh. I really like it. I would like to appreciate their work. I will recommend others too to visit this location. I love it.

People are so kind with their customers. I really appreciate their quick service and my food was so fresh and hot. Specially, Gursimran one of the employee I met in drive through she treated me and my family very politely and gave our food quickly. I would like to recommend others to visit this location once. Great work
All the best

A very huge thank you to the staff at this location, in particular a staff member named Nimrat Gill. I had an issue with my order and this staff member quickly resolved the issue. She was very kind, polite and empathetic. Thank you for being so fast and efficient in resolving my issue.

Super nice employees! I love the morning ladies . They always have my order ready to go. Thank you Sunita, Sara and Kamal and Julia. You ladies are very fast!!! I always go to this mcds because of their service

I wanted to let you guys know how hard-working the weekend team is. Simrit is a very hardworking manager and has excellent customer service skills. My order was missing an item because it did not get rung in correctly. Simrit promptly not only apologized & fixed it but actually took interest in my concern which made me feel very welcomed. From now on, I will be a regular weekend customer along with my family. Thank you Simrit, may God bless you. Cathy.
People are so kind with their customers. I really like their quick service. They are serving fresh and good food. Mostly I visit their with my friends and I enjoy my meal. Great work
These ladies working on weekdays mornings are just awesome! Great service and right order everytime Get my morning Latte everyday from there

Good some time better,even best but sometimes bitter, because of service order in delays..overall   ok. Vegetarian options: Yes, but u need to check out according to locations ..all have some differ. Dietary restrictions: Yes. Parking: Good and all spair. Kid-friendliness: Pretty much. Wheelchair accessibility: Ofcourse more.

Big SHOUT to Brandon(girl manager on sept 14 9pm 2021) If you see this thank you for being manager because someone needs to learn. She was the second manager I talked to and was understanding. The first one I talked to told me to hold and passed me over to Brandon. Brandon did a good job of understanding what the situation was. Ps: Sorry if I spelled your name wrong Ps: To the other manager if you see this I hope you learn stuff Ps: I give 5 stars to the manager not to the store for she did the right thing at the right time My parents always get told off because they cant understand people and today there was something wrong with the order in which they actually give a coupon and showed the cashier what they wanted but they did the wrong order and was quite rude about not changing it for them.(they did in the end but it was still more expensive when they asked for a different burger) My parents told me when they got home. And I was livid with this happening at McDonald when they should be trained better then anyone. I know for a fact there training for staff is great so dont know where customer service went with some of the people in the store!!!

Staff were friendly and sociable, and food was delivered fast and to the T as to what I ordered, going as far as to even inquire if I needed any ketchup or sauces. (no other locations have asked this question before) A wonderful option for those in the area!

Son had the spicy Szechuan chicken and I had the ghost pepper. Better than expected. Son also gave it a big thumbs up. We got some, you should too.

It was McDonalds right! They were fast , polite and didnt take too long to get someone to open washroom door. Happy to say they were on their toes , checking all fast food reasturants for Google maps is a pleasure for me.
